%F A249862 a(n) = 3^(n-1)*(3*S(n, 34/3) - 17*S(n-1, 34/3)), n >= 0, with the scaled Chebyshev S sequence 3^n*S(n, 34/3) given in A248163.
%F A249862 O.g.f.: (1 - 17*x)/(1 - 34*x + 9*x^2).
%F A249862 a(n) = 34*a(n-1) - 9*a(n-2), a(0) = 0, a(1) = 17.
